OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1782497914
OL,3,CHuge beach fight prompts new measures
OL,4,Cto clamp down on anti-social behaviour
OL,6,FNew measures are being introduced to
OL,7,Fclamp down on anti-social behaviour in
OL,8,FBroadstairs and Margate following a
OL,9,Fspate of recent incidents at beaches
OL,10,Fduring the hot weather.
OL,12,FSeveral people were arrested and large
OL,13,Fgatherings of people were dispersed by
OL,14,Fpolice on Wednesday - one of the
OL,15,Fhottest June days on record.
OL,17,FA fight broke out on the beach at
OL,18,FViking Bay in Broadstairs involving a
OL,19,Fsmall group of people, which resulted
OL,20,Fin a man in his 20s suffering a cut to
OL,21,Fhis head.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
