FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1782497914
OL,3,CHuge beach fight prompts new measures
OL,4,Cto clamp down on anti-social behaviour
OL,6,FAn 18-year-old man from London, an 18-
OL,7,Fyear-old man from Swanley and a 16-
OL,8,Fyear-old boy from Dartford were all
OL,9,Farrested on suspicion of assault.
OL,11,FIn Margate, patrols were called to
OL,12,Freports of further fighting on the
OL,13,Fbeach.
OL,15,FAn 18-year-old man from London who
OL,16,Fpolice believe had been throwing
OL,17,Fpunches at numerous people tried to
OL,18,Frun away from officers but was caught
OL,19,Fa short time later and taken into
OL,20,Fcustody.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1782497914
OL,3,CHuge beach fight prompts new measures
OL,4,Cto clamp down on anti-social behaviour
OL,6,FPolice also responded to a disturbance
OL,7,Fat the town's railway station where
OL,8,Fseveral people including a security
OL,9,Fguard were reported to have been
OL,10,Fassaulted.
OL,12,FAn 18-year-old man from London was
OL,13,Farrested on suspicion of affray.
OL,15,FA Public Space Protection Order will
OL,16,Fbe put in place for three years from
OL,17,Fnext week and is being backed by local
OL,18,FMP Pollington Billington.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1782497914
OL,3,CHuge beach fight prompts new measures
OL,4,Cto clamp down on anti-social behaviour
OL,6,FShe's called on the Home Secretary,
OL,7,FShabana Mahmood, for more action to
OL,8,Ftackle things like crime, littering
OL,9,Fand illegal parking especially during
OL,10,Fthe summer tourist season.
OL,12,FChief Inspector Ian Swallow, District
OL,13,FCommander for Thanet, said: "We have
OL,14,Fmade it very clear that we will not
OL,15,Ftolerate antisocial behaviour in our
OL,16,Fcoastal towns this summer or at any
OL,17,Fother time of the year, and as
OL,18,Fdemonstrated by these incidents we
OL,19,Fwill quickly make arrests and move
OL,20,Fpeople on when necessary.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1782497914
OL,3,CHuge beach fight prompts new measures
OL,4,Cto clamp down on anti-social behaviour
OL,6,F"If people cannot enjoy the warm
OL,7,Fweather without fighting or causing a
OL,8,Fnuisance to others then they should
OL,9,Fstay at home, otherwise they will be
OL,10,Fforced to go home or could find
OL,11,Fthemselves in custody.
OL,13,F"Our beaches are some of the most
OL,14,Fbeautiful in the UK and it is
OL,15,Finevitable that large numbers of
OL,16,Fpeople including parents with young
OL,17,Fchildren will travel here to make the
OL,18,Fmost of the high temperatures.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1782497914
OL,3,CHuge beach fight prompts new measures
OL,4,Cto clamp down on anti-social behaviour
OL,6,F"It is unacceptable that a minority of
OL,7,Ftroublemakers will ruin the enjoyment
OL,8,Fof others because they do not know how
OL,9,Fto behave, and we will not stand for
OL,10,Fit.
OL,12,F"We will continue to have a highly
OL,13,Fvisible presence in our coastal towns
OL,14,Ffor the rest of this week and
OL,15,Fthroughout the summer, and dispersal
OL,16,Forders remain in place in Margate,
OL,17,FBroadstairs, Ramsgate and Westwood
OL,18,FCross.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1782497914
OL,3,CHuge beach fight prompts new measures
OL,4,Cto clamp down on anti-social behaviour
OL,6,F"This will help to keep any further
OL,7,Fdisorder to a minimum and prevent it
OL,8,Ffrom occurring in the first place."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
